						<summary>

						<p>On a Nāga-stone set up in a street.</p>						

						<p>Velanāḍu Choḍas: Kulōttuṅga Rājēndrachōḍa.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Records the gift of lands to the temple of Sōmēśvaradēva at Abū[ru] in Koṇḍapaḍumaṟa by certain Reḍḍis for the merit of Kulōttuṅga Rājendra-Chōḍarāja, on the occasion of Uttarāyaṇa Saṅkrānti.</p>						

